value.name: Cocaine, Prison & Likes: Isabelle's True Story
value.original_name: Cocaïne, prison & likes : la vraie histoire d'Isabelle
value.overview: In 2016, Isabelle Lagacé and Mélina Roberge are arrested for importing cocaine aboard a cruise ship in Australia. The news made the headlines around the world. How does a young woman get involved in an international drug trafficking network?
